-4dCKx3qosE1pyTZl3Q">Tầm Tây Sơn ẩn giả bất ngộ - 尋西山隱者不遇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2u-Vi/author-e3_4xASNBFssHXU5aeQgsw">Khâu Vi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A3o/T%C3%BAc-s%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-c0QzxCX5wk1TUk7G8U8zNw">Túc sơn tự - 宿山寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A3o/author-zlEhGhvit8FPpDIsa8T0QA">Giả Đảo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/Y%C3%AAn-T%E1%BB%AD-s%C6%A1n-Long-%C4%90%E1%BB%99ng-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-XIAZPy3QVGoej-LjrvPRng">Yên Tử sơn Long Động tự - 安子山龍洞寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-n8TXz8ZnEQ2g7U6IvK74Vw">Nguyễn Trung Ngạn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/Y%E1%BA%BFt-H%C3%A0nh-nh%E1%BA%A1c-mi%E1%BA%BFu-to%E1%BA%A1i-t%C3%BAc-nh%E1%BA%A1c-t%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-m%C3%B4n-l%C3%A2u/poem-Fi0Gv61h-zHA0H8Q_95dwg">Yết Hành nhạc miếu toại túc nhạc tự đề môn lâu - 謁衡岳廟遂宿嶽寺題門樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
